<h4><a href="https://www.nobelprize.org/prizes/economic-sciences/2020/summary/">2020 年诺贝尔经济学奖公布</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1371246" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/0b2a-kakmcxe2000693.jpg" alt="" width="1000" height="1000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/0b2a-kakmcxe2000693.jpg 1000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/0b2a-kakmcxe2000693-360x360.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/0b2a-kakmcxe2000693-768x768.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" /></p>
<p>2020 年诺贝尔经济学奖颁给了两位来自美国的经济学家 Paul R. Milgrom 和 Robert B. Wilson。他们的获奖理由为「对拍卖理论的改进以及新拍卖形式的发明」。</p>
<h4><a href="https://weibo.com/1687422352/JoOoJqVis?from=page_1006061687422352_profile&amp;wvr=6&amp;mod=weibotime&amp;type=comment#_rnd1602497574990">肯德基在六个城市上线植物肉产品</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1371247" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/001QcfDyly1gjlpvm3l6xj60u01e6npg02.jpg" alt="" width="690" height="1154" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/001QcfDyly1gjlpvm3l6xj60u01e6npg02.jpg 690w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/001QcfDyly1gjlpvm3l6xj60u01e6npg02-360x602.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/001QcfDyly1gjlpvm3l6xj60u01e6npg02-612x1024.jpg 612w" sizes="(max-width: 690px) 100vw, 690px" /></p>
<p>昨天，肯德基宣布在上海、北京、广州、深圳、杭州和武汉的 210 家餐厅上线植物肉产品「植世代牛肉芝士汉堡」和「植世代黄金鸡块」，售价分别为 35 元和 11 元。</p>
<h4><a href="https://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-features/first-look-louis-vuitton-x-nba-capsule-collection-collaboration-1234630680/">LV 发布 NBA 联名系列</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1371248" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/nba.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="717" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/nba.jpg 1200w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/nba-360x215.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/nba-768x459.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/nba-1024x612.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>
